Class LicenseValidatorStrictTest

java.lang.Object
  com.soebes.maven.plugins.mlv.TestBase
      com.soebes.maven.plugins.mlv.licenses.LicenseValidatorStrictTest

public class LicenseValidatorStrictTest
extends TestBase

The intention of this test is to check if the comparsion only based on name and/or on URL of the license is working correctly with activated strictChecking option. That means both name and url must part of the licenses.xml file.

Author:
Karl Heinz Marbaise
